A method call in ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/exec/tez/CustomPartitionVertex.java is mispelled causing a compilation failure when building against Hadoop-2.x.

Line 681 of the patch is:

+    int totalResource = context.getTotalAVailableResource().getMemory();

but should be:

+    int totalResource = context.getTotalAvailableResource().getMemory();
